CRUISE_HEADER.CRUISE_NAME _1: Echantillonnage à une station fixe dans l'ESL
CRUISE_HEADER.CRUISE_DESCRIPTION _1: Monitorage des communautes planctoniques (zoo et phyto) et de l'environnement marin dans le chenal Laurentien au large de Rimouski

QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_7: Test 1.7: IML Unlikely Position - Outside Canadian Waters

QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_15: Test 2.9: Excessive Gradient or Inversion (TEMP, PSAL, NTRZ, PHOS, PHPH, TALK) (512)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_16: Test 2.10: Surface Dissolved Oxygen Data versus Percent Saturation (1024)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_17: Test 3.5: Petrie Monthly Climatology (TEMP, PSAL, SIGT)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_18: Test 3.6: Brickman Monthly Climatology (NTRA, PHOS, SLCA)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_19: Test 5.2: Ratio and Profile Visual Inspection (station data)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_20: Test 5.3: Replicates Visual Inspection (whole cruise data)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_21: Test 5.4: Bottle Versus CTD Measurements Visual Inspection (whole cruise data)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_22: Test 5.5: Ratio and Profile Visual Inspection (whole cruise data)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_TESTS_23: Test 5.6: Variable patterns with time (whole cruise data)
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_COMMENTS_1: QCFF values are derived from tests of the bottle quality control stage 2
QUALITY_HEADER.QUALITY_COMMENTS_2: A quality flag modified by hand has a QCFF value of 1
